= Mailer Logger

Extends Mailer with logging functionality.

== Install

1. copy this code into vendor/extensions, e.g. by doing +git submodule add git://github.com/tricycle/radiant-mailer-logger-extension.git vendor/extensions/mailer_logger+
2. From the app root type this command:

  rake radiant:extensions:mailer_logger:update

Which will copy some needed files to the public directory of your app.

